data.description: Stunning views of Denver from this 15rh floor remodeled condo in the heart of Capitol Hill.  Newly updated kitchen and bath with quartz counters and modern subway tiles.  New designer stainless kitchen appliances have just been installed.  The walk-in shower has a glass enclosure and beautiful hexagon marble tile, 2 sinks.  Large bedroom with bay window, new carpet and 2 custom closets.  Large living | dining area with new wide plank flooring that leads to the oversized balcony.  Washer, Dryer Hookups in utility closet as well as a wet bar hookup in the living room.  Heat and water paid by HOA.  Underground secured parking.  Penn Square Condominiums is a secure building and has some of the best amenities in Cap Hill;  including a fitness center, pool, guest suite, plenty of guest parking, rooftop lounges with access to a panoramic city | mountain views and main floor party room. Within Blocks, you will find an array of restaurants, coffee shops, Ideal Market, Trader Joe's, Cheesman Park, Denver Botanical Gardens, the Denver Art Museum, and Cherry Creek trail access. Don't miss the chance to own this exquisite home in a vibrant neighborhood.  Seller will help with a 2-1 buy down
